  "detailed_description": "<h1>bilibili Publisher Sale</h1><p>Up to 70% off! Great Bundle Offer and a unique Early Access Wuxia game, all at bilibili Publisher Sale 2023! Click on me to access the Sale Page<br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/bef9a525304213162f2c463c690cb19f.poster.avif?t=1755751193\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/bef9a525304213162f2c463c690cb19f.webm?t=1755751193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/bef9a525304213162f2c463c690cb19f.mp4?t=1755751193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界观</h2>20XX年，随着科技的不断发展，地球资源逐渐枯竭，政治形势紧张。<br>这时，一家以生物科技起家的新能源公司【瑞恩梅克生物科技】，研发出了【分子重构技术】。<br>这一技术的问世彻底改变了世界。<br>为了争夺这个可以点石成金的尖端科技，人类开始了漫长的战争。<br>最终，【瑞恩梅克生物科技】将【分子重构技术】投入战争，彻底摧毁其他势力，取得了最终的胜利。<br>他们运用【分子重构技术】建立起【新都市】。<br>若干年后，在人类世界最后的净土上，一个看似普通的学生，化作了网络世界的“幽灵，无意中碰触了这个世界的”禁忌“……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色声优</h2>4位虚拟人物声优信息 <br><br>温柔大哥哥 叶别枝：中(吴韬）/日(木村良平）<br>人气偶像 桃杏：中(沈念如）/日(佐仓绫音）<br>富豪少爷 弥久：中(路扬）/日(铃木达央）<br>武斗派少女 司鲸：中(贺文潇）/日(石川由依）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/18585fe0f49c213dc25b6d8ed7baa7d5.avif?t=1755751193\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色养成</h2>创造培养虚拟人物，随着人格与信息的不断完善，或许你所创造的人物将也不在仅仅是“虚拟”的存在。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/46910735ca7f6a781ae664747b326405.poster.avif?t=1755751193\" width=616 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/46910735ca7f6a781ae664747b326405.webm?t=1755751193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/46910735ca7f6a781ae664747b326405.mp4?t=1755751193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >黑客系统</h2>玩家所扮演的主角掌握着顶级的黑客技术，在这世界中你将可以入侵到任意设备与网络中，骇客入侵对于你来说不过只是一个小小的“游戏”。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/fd58cba0f6a59c1c73bf3a4a94af5682.poster.avif?t=1755751193\" width=616 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/fd58cba0f6a59c1c73bf3a4a94af5682.webm?t=1755751193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/fd58cba0f6a59c1c73bf3a4a94af5682.mp4?t=1755751193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独立事件</h2>玩家在游戏内会收到形色各异的求助信息，你可以选择无视这些信息，也可以使用自己的能力去帮助他们。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108320/extras/a8a068d1ea3ddb230ef67fe5d2abfb4a.avif?t=1755751193\" width=616 height=900 /></span>",
